  • 2.4/5ghz Bual Dand Wifi Light Bulb Camera: The latest 5G & 2.4G dual-band light bulb security cameras wireless outdoor have stronger signal reception, higher stability, longer distance to use, no lag and smoother real-time video compared to traditional 2.4G single-band lightbulb security camera. Simply screw the best light bulb security camera into the equipped E27/E26 bulb base (AC110/240V) and plug it into a power outlet, connect bulb camera to your home wifi via app EseeCloud.
  • 2K HD & Full Color Day and Night Vision: light bulb security camera 360 supports 2K HD image, which is clearer than 1080P. Porch light cameras for home security ensuring you can see ultra-clear details both day and night. Outdoor camera wireless supports color/smart/infrared night vision mode. Whether in the faint starlight or complete darkness, proch light security camera can ensure clear image of objects within 33 ft.
  • Two-Way Audio & Real-Time Alerts: Screw in camera for light socket outdoor built-in microphone and speaker support two-way language real-time call, communicate with your family or visitors without any obstacles, realize face-to-face communication. Light socket security camera can set up an audible alarm, when detecting moving objects, sightbulb camera will emit a loud alarm sound and white light at the same time. Scaring away intruder and protecting the family safety.
  • Motion Detection & Body Detection Alarm: The bulb camera 360 degree wifi outdoor equipped with a highly sensitive motion sensor that supports horizontal rotation of 355° and vertical flip of 90°, realizing 360 degree blind spot-free super wide-range accurate detection and tracking of objects. If you turn on human body detection alarm in APP, once 5g security camera 360 detects human body movement, bulb camera will record the movement and notify you via APP,thus reducing false alarms.
  • Multi User Sharing & Smart Storage: Lightbulb camera 360 degree wifi outdoor supports multiple users to watch videos. You can share the device with your family and friends for simultaneous monitoring through the app. Light bulb cameras for home security storage supports cloud storage (paid access required) and up to 128G micro SD card storage.Outdoor Bullet camera is Alexa compatible, easy to install and simple to operate.

    • Free 2B Me
      5.0 out of 5 starsVerified Purchase
      Light socket Cameras
      Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2024
      I absolutely love these cameras. The cameras are pretty easy to use and set up was really easy. I like that there are two cameras in the package. My cameras are black, but I seem to recall having a choice of black or white. I like the black because they are not as... See more
      I absolutely love these cameras. The cameras are pretty easy to use and set up was really easy. I like that there are two cameras in the package. My cameras are black, but I seem to recall having a choice of black or white. I like the black because they are not as noticeable. I have the two cameras side by side, pointed in different directions. The cameras are really easy to control with the app on your phone. You do have a choice of storing your videos in their cloud, for a monthly fee, or you can store your videos on an SD card kept in your camera.

      There was some confusion for me with the videos and storage and viewing. I sent a message to support and received a response fairly quickly. We went back and forth multiple times and support kept answering until my questions were answered and all issues resolved. I even received an email a few weeks later asking if everything was still okay with my cameras and making sure everything was working. And assuring me if I have any more issues to just email and let them know and they will work with me until everything is resolved.

      A couple of things it took me a little bit to figure out - if you are just using the SD card, which I do, as this is sufficient for me, if you click "events" you will only be able to view apx 10 seconds of your video. But if you click playback and then SD card you can view your entire video. You are able to set the camera to event record, meaning it will only record if motion is detected or you can record all the time. You are also able to set the sensitivity of how easily the camera is triggered. The camera also records sound and you are able to talk to the person at your door thru the app. I have never used this feature but would be nice if I wanted to use it.

      The camera will support up to a 128 gb micro sd card. Once the card is full the videos will record over themselves and will replace the oldest videos first. I also like that I am able to hit the record on the app on my phone and make the camera start recording.

      I would definitely recommend these cameras and would purchase these same cameras in the future if I ever have any more available light sockets. Oh and that is another super awesome great thing. All you have to do is screw this camera into a light socket just like a light bulb. These cameras can be used outdoors. Mine are screwed into a light socket that is outside. It is under the eve of the house so it is not soaked with water but I am sure does get wet when it rains and the wind blows. And so far it has not hurt the camera at all.
